sequenceDiagram
    participant A as 클라이언트 A
    participant WS as WebSocket<br/>(STOMP)
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant B as 클라이언트 B
    participant DB as MySQL

    A->>WS: CONNECT (Authorization: Bearer JWT)
    B->>WS: CONNECT (Authorization: Bearer JWT)
    A->>WS: SUBSCRIBE /topic/chatroom.{roomId}
    B->>WS: SUBSCRIBE /topic/chatroom.{roomId}

    Note over A,DB: 메시지 전송
    A->>WS: SEND /app/chat.message {content}
    WS->>DB: ChatMessage 저장
    WS->>MQ: publish → chatroom.{roomId} exchange
    MQ-->>WS: consume (AMQP)
    WS-->>A: broadcast (STOMP)
    WS-->>B: broadcast (STOMP)

    Note over DB: 오프라인 사용자 푸시 알림
    WS->>DB: INSERT push<br/>(type=CHAT, memberId, content)
